  <title>Gio.ActionGroup::action-enabled-changed</title>
  <synopsis><code mime="text/x-gjs">
connect('action-enabled-changed', function (actionGroup, action_name: String, enabled: Boolean, ): void);
  </code></synopsis>
  <p>Signals that the enabled status of the named action has changed.</p>
  <p>Since 2.28</p>
<terms>
<item>
<title><code>actionGroup</code></title>
<p>instance of <link xref="Gio.ActionGroup"/> that is emitting the signal</p>
</item>
<item>
<title><code>action_name</code></title>
  <p>the name of the action in @action_group</p>
</item>
<item>
<title><code>enabled</code></title>
  <p>whether the action is enabled or not</p>
</item>
</terms>

